<tbody><tr><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-1"><div dir="ltr"><h2><a name="TOC-Event-driven-and-time-driven-controls"></a>Event-driven and time-driven controls</h2>
<div><b>Event-driven controls</b> happen when something specific happens, say the creation of an Exception Report. Event based controls mean a decision has to be made.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div><b>Time-driven controls</b> are predefined and normal such as Highlight Reports and Checklist Reports. Interesting though they may be chances are nothing changes much - just a confirmation that all is well. It is an opportunity to check that these controls are indeed in place though and assurance is the name of the game.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
